Text.string: Whoa, you hijacked the War Pig?! Well, I guess grab a bobblehead off the dashboard or somethin' to prove you got it! That should work.
Looks like Puttergunk locked that place up tight. There's gotta be some way to get that door open.
Hahaha! What the God-Queen meant to say is, why do you think you have what it takes to be our new Mouthpiece?
Because I'm real loud! And I love the God-Queen more than anyone!
You lie! Gorebox am the God-Queen's most devoted follower! I'll kill you to prove it!
Sure. Fight to the death. I'm into it.
My rectum! Aghhh!
Huh. Never seen a dislocated ass before.
Loving it. Loving it!
These people are insane.
What is wrong with these people?
This is madness.
These guys are weird.
Look around. Maybe you can shut off the power somehow.
Okay, let's get this thing movin' again. Who's next?
Some mouth-breather named Blargmaw. So, why should you be our new Mouthpiece?
What?
Ugh. Are you here to audition to be the next Mouthpiece?
What?
I'm boredddd. Someone kill himmmm.
I'll whip you bloody... with your own spine!
Now THAT'S the kind of fire we're lookin' for! Tch, but, no second chances in showbiz! Finish him.
Got a new way for you to stick it to the COV!
You see a generator or somethin' nearby?
This guy seems to fit the bill.
Yeah. Maybe. Whatever.
Yes! The God-Queen should name ME the new Mouthpiece!
I'm sorry, did you just tell me what I should DO?! End him. Now.
What? No! I—I'm sorry! I didn't mean to!
Drop your offerings or get blasted!
Nice offerings! Hey, what's your favorite thing about God-Queen Tyreen?
I dig her coat. Want it!
I like her tattoos. Kinda hot.
Her glorious pelt.
Her... can-do attitude.
WHAT?! A Vault Thief! Kill them!
Those filthy Vault Thieves murdered our most favorite Mouthpiece—so we've got an opening!
Uh-oh! We've got some Vault Thieves trying to interrupt our auditions. Go kill 'em for me!
Ahem! For us.
Oh nooo... you killed a few followers... woe is meeee...
Where will we ever find more?
Oh right. Like, everywhere. Toodles!
Losers.
Guh. Idiots.
Pricks.
Stupid kids.
Prove your loyalty to earn your place in the auditions. Steal the Hammerclan's Banner, blow up the War Pigs' War Pig, and, uh... I dunno, loot Puttergunk's strongbox.
Grhrgrhrhhh...
Them COV are tryin' to find a new Mouthpiece. Let's stop 'em.

Since you went and wasted the big-talkin' Mouthpiece, the Calypsos are castin' for a new loudmouth. Whaddya say we interrupt them tryouts? With bullets. But first, we need to get you an audition. Go track down the entry requirements.
Once we get you into those auditions, you can waste ALL them wannabe Mouthpieces.
Sounds like you know what you gotta do to crash those tryouts. Get to it, Vault Hunter!
Since you wasted that big-talkin' Mouthpiece, the Calypsos are casting for a new loudmouth. Whaddya say we interrupt the tryouts? With bullets. But first, we need to get you into the auditions.
Bring your special offerings to the Holy Broadcasting Center or we'll kill you on sight! Good luck!
Yeah, I always hated the Hammerclan. Go grab that banner!
Huh, banner's pretty high up there, VH. Start climbin'!
Hey, nice! You got it!
Man, that War Pig rig is not messing around. But I know you can thrash that thing!
That War Pig is fast, amigo. You might need a vehicle to hunt down that hoss.
Very cool, VH. Now grab a hunk of War Pig and we'll be all set!
Whoa, you hijacked the War Pig?! I mean, that's badass and all, but you're still gon' have to blow it up.
That'll prove you blasted the War Pig! Heh, sweet.
I don't even WANNA know what kinda stuff you're gonna find in that weirdo's strongbox.
What is... y'know what? Nevermind. I definitely don't want to know what that is. Eugh!
Hit that generator to shut off the power to the door, VH.
The Calypsos are broadcasting their auditions live. Let's check it out.
Looks like the Calypsos are broadcasting another audition.
You got all those audition requirements? Good stuff, VH. Now head to the Holy Broadcast Center, it's showtime!
Didn't I already clear that place out?
Excuse me, but didn't I already handle all the COV at the HBC? Also, too many acronyms.
I was under the impression I already cleansed that place of their filth. With gusto.
Didn't I already kill everyone in that place?
Well... yeah. But don't you wanna blast some more bandits, or what?
Annnnd, there's another audition going out over the ECHOnet.
I think that got the door open! You should be able to raid Puttergunk's place now. Not that I envy that task, like, at all.
Me too! The Great Vault beckons! Come on in!
Now get in there and don't leave any of them Mouthpiece-wannabes alive!
You know what? We're running out of time, so—what's your deal, big guy?
Well, I look and sound exactly like the last guy!
Sold! Looks like we've got our new Mouthpiece! Yay!
Yes, God-Queen. I will be your war-scream!
'Kay. Great. First task, kill the Vault Thief!
Well, looks like we didn't make it in time to stop the castin', but we can still take out that new Mouthpiece!
Eh, those two are like varkid larva—don't let 'em get under your skin. Seriously.
You know, I heard that Mouthpiece fella kept a stash somewhere near his organ. Maybe give them keys a tickle and see what happens.
Comin' at you live from the Holy Broadcasting Center, our first Mouthpiece contestant is... Stank Knee! Holy hell, what is wrong with your knee?
Ooh, secret stashes and stuff. Sweet. Look around!
There you go! Good find! Now come on back.
Nice audition! Haha! Y'know, sometimes the best way to shut someone up is to shoot 'em in the face. Good work, VH!
